des: "Zesty and highly-aromatic pizza seasoning that makes your house smell like an Italian pizza parlor! Sprinkle this over pizza or tops of stromboli the last 10 minutes of baking time."
ins: Stir the Parmesan cheese, Italian seasoning, poultry seasoning, cumin, and garlic powder together in a mixing bowl. Store in an airtight container in refrigerator up to 2 months.
